{{Vgname2|即时战术游戏|en=Real-time tactics|缩写“RTT”<ref name="ign-stateoftherts">{{cite web|url=http://pc.ign.com/articles/700/700747p3.html|title=The State of the RTS|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=7 April 2006|accessdate=14 September 2006|archive-date=2006-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060624224943/http://pc.ign.com/articles/700/700747p3.html|dead-url=no}}(Article at IGN discussing their perception of RTS and related genres as of 2006. RTT is discussed as a new and not yet established genre from the publisher's perspective.)</ref>}}是一种[[电子游戏类型|电子游戏类型]]，它属于[[戰爭遊戲|战术战争游戏]]，玩家以实时的方式在模拟的战场环境中进行战术指挥。它和[[即时战略|即时战略]]不同的就是没有了经典的资源采集和建筑建造过程，更強調各種兵種的重要性<ref name="ign-stateoftherts" /><ref name="splanet">{{cite web | title =Point - CounterPoint: Resource Collection vs. Fixed Units | publisher =StrategyPlanet | url =http://www.strategyplanet.com/features/articles/pcp-resources/ | accessdate =2007-11-04 | deadurl =yes | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20071231194439/http://www.strategyplanet.com/features/articles/pcp-resources/ | archivedate =2007-12-31 }}</ref>並專注於战术上的使用。

== 与即时战略的比较 ==
总的来说[[战略|战略]]指的是范围相当广的武器的运用，以及外交、情报、经济资源的使用；而[[战术|战术]]则只关注近期的一场战役的胜负。<ref name=gspytbsrts_pvi>{{cite web |last=Walker |first=Mark |title=Strategy Gaming: Part VI -- Where the Genre is Headed |publisher=[[GameSpy|GameSpy]] |url=http://archive.gamespy.com/articles/february02/stratfinal/ |date=February 2002 |accessdate=2010-02-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071030014041/http://archive.gamespy.com/articles/february02/stratfinal/ |archivedate=2007-10-30 }}</ref>而到了电子游戏领域，这个差别通常只体现在有没有建筑和单位的生产上面。<ref name="gama_goodfellow">{{cite web  | last = Goodfellow  | first = Troy  | title = The Future Of The RTS - A Counter-Opinion  | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]  | date = January 28, 2008  | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=17098  | accessdate = 2010-02-02  | archive-date = 2009-11-10  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20091110150135/http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=17098  | dead-url = no  }}</ref>

